PARTE 2 || Gracias México por el amor, por esos entrenos tan lindos con mi familia crossfitera, por las fiestas, por el apoyo de las personas, y por tanta comida rica… Más en PARTE 3

PARTE 3 || Y terminando con un salpicón de fotos y videos, una vez más, gracias México. Regresaré? Of course my horse. Estaré de aquí para allá, y me seguirán viendo, y riendo, y disfrutando. No me olviden. Nos vemos pronto 🤍🇲🇽

Last week was a blast 💥 🤍

My dad came to visit me, and God let me show him what I’ve been working so hard for: give my family back everything they gave me in my life.

We went to water ski, outlet malls (yeah, a very latin american activity to do in the US), the beach, and a lot of fun things. It totally reloaded me with energy and purpose.

He want back to Colombia crying, proud of his son, but well, I’m the one proud of him 🤍. You can see on the last slide the sing he always sings to me, and the one I listen to when feeling down (and it makes me cry)

Love you dad; jt was the first trip abroad together, but definitely not the last one 🤍

🛑 🛑  @sarelly.sarelly @true_________________
